  "title": "addNumericRefinement does not allow multiple operators",
  "body": "I want to put multiple numeric filters with different operators and do an or between all of them.\r\n\r\n# Currently \r\n\r\n```helper.addNumericRefinement('rooms', '=', ['42', '56', '37'] ).search();```\r\n\r\n# Expected \r\n\r\n```helper.addNumericRefinement('rooms',  ['=42', '=56', '>=37'] ).search();```",
